description: “No Jodas” is a Cuban truck serving Bomb Ass food to a hungry world. We are committed to serving truly excellent Cuban fare to both newcomers and Cuban critics alike.Born out of necessity to serve the best Cuban food this side of Miami, No Jodas Cuban Kitchen started with Rob’s love for cooking that began with his mother teaching him all she knew. He has been fortunate to be part of a Cuban family that has a long and rich tradition in cooking.  Both Mother and Grandmother have given up their secrets, straight from Cuba, to enrich his cooking abilities.Life can be funny, sometimes you turn around and your dreams come true! Thus “No Jodas Cuban Kitchen” is born.Enjoy!
name: No Jodas Cuban Kitchen
